      "  [3] FFL motif rows                   : 4436\n",
      "  [4] Fully mapped FFL rows            : 4436\n",
      "  [5] Sum of all total_synapses        : 43031\n",
      "  [6] Sum of all hyperedge weights w_e : 9800.1540\n",
